		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;198&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;475px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.jaredszajkowski.com/2024/01/simple-incremental-bash-backup-script/02_Year_directory.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1038&#34;
